    <h3 id="tc-1"><span class="section-number">1</span> About Our Service</h3>

    <p>They Made Me is a UK-based genealogy research service. We take the information you provide about your family — names, dates, and places — and research your ancestry using a combination of:</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Historical record databases</strong> including FamilySearch.org (operated by The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints) and FreeBMD (an index of civil registration records for England and Wales).</li>
        <li><strong>Artificial intelligence tools</strong> (OpenAI's GPT-4o and Anthropic's Claude) to review, cross-reference, and validate the research findings.</li>
        <li><strong>Manual review</strong> by our research team to verify results and resolve ambiguities.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Our products include family tree fan charts (delivered as high-quality PDF files), GEDCOM data files (the universal standard for genealogy data), and accompanying research reports. The specific deliverables depend on the package you order.</p>


